      <article class="panel span-12 workspace-panel" data-routing-workspace="modes"><h2><span>Режимы клиентов</span></h2><div class="table-shell" id="routeModesTable"></div></article>
      <article class="panel span-12 workspace-panel" data-routing-workspace="readiness"><h2><span>Готовность чувствительных RU</span></h2><div class="table-shell" id="trustedReadinessTable"></div></article>
